snippet.title: Iron Harvest - "Tech & Controls Demo"
snippet.description:
NOW ON KICKSTARTER: http://www.iron-harvest.com/kickstarter

Here are some impressions from our internal Iron Harvest "Tech & Controls Demo".

Setting up all the systems correctly takes a lot of time. But a strong base is crucial for an ambitious RTS like Iron Harvest. We're looking forward to show you guys real gameplay in the upcoming months.
